title: Syllabus mentioned in ERP
text: Identification and Physical description; Specific gravity; Mechanical analysis; Proctor s Compaction test; Permeability - Constant head, Variable head; Direct Shear test - Cohesionless soil, Cohesive soil; Unconfined Compression test; Triaxial test - Undrained, Drained; Triaxial test with pore pressure measurements; Vane Shear test.
